---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — CuloTon"
  description="About CuloTon, an independent news platform covering the TON blockchain ecosystem."
>
  <article class="news-article">
    <h1>About CuloTon</h1>

    <p class="article-summary">
      CuloTon is an independent English-language news platform covering the TON blockchain ecosystem.
    </p>

    <div class="body">
      <p>
        We track protocol upgrades, DeFi activity, payments, Telegram integrations, mini-apps, validator news,
        and the broader culture forming around the network. Our coverage is sourced from reputable industry
        publications, official TON Foundation channels, and on-chain analytics, with original articles credited
        and linked back to the source.
      </p>

      <p>
        CuloTon is brought to you by the community behind <strong style="color: var(--accent);">$CULO</strong>,
        a memecoin native to the TON network. We believe in a TON ecosystem that is both serious about technology
        and not afraid to have fun.
      </p>

      <p>
        Found a story we missed? Have a tip? Want to advertise? Reach out — we'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
